query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('archive',
'esp8266',
'factorial',
'flink-streaming',
'innerhtml',
'java-11',
'logout',
'minecraft',
'orbeon',
'resolution',
'statsmodels',
'windows-server-2012');
